data.description: New Roof 2018 Priced to sell this property in Winter Park will not last long. New AC in 2019. New Water Heater in 2019. This beautiful home is perfect for a first time buyer or as investment. 2 bedroom home with office.  Why pay rent when this gardeners paradise is ready for you to call home? If you’re looking for carefree  living but don't want to give up your green space, this is the perfect property! As you enter through the gates of this charming condo you will find a sweet outdoor porch with built in planters waiting for your green thumb.  The living area and outdoor space make entertaining a joy. Beautiful  kitchen perfect for entertaining makes cooking a pleasure. This space has been completely updated with new cabinets and stainless steel appliances and granite countertops. The property has two bedrooms with generous closet space and a full bath. Residents enjoy a community pool and tennis courts. This great location is close to all that downtown Orlando has to offer. It is close to shopping, sports venues, and the Dr. Phillips Center. Come see this beauty while it lasts!
